'''''Star Wars Insider'' 52''' is the fifty-second issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was the first issue produced by editor [[Jeff Quick]], following the departure of [[Dan Madsen]], the original ''Star Wars Insider'' publisher and former president of [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|The Official ''Star Wars'' Fan Club]], and longtime Editor-in-Chief [[Jon Bradley Snyder]]. At the same time, longtime Managing Editor [[Scott Chernoff]], who had been overseeing the magazine, offered some continuity to the transition, becoming a Contributing Editor. Issue 52 was published on [[February 27]], [[2001]].

