*"[[DecipherCon 2000]]" &mdash; Deal With It! {{C|by Rich Handley}}
*"[[Dear 2-1B]]"
*"[[The Last Page]]"

===Features===
*"[[George Lucas: The Story Comes First]]" {{C|by [[Scott Chernoff]]}}
*:<small>The ''Insider'' talks with the man who started it all. George candidly discusses the darkness of the story he's telling, the phenomenon that ''Star Wars'' has become, and why so many bad movies get made.</small>
*"[[Casting Director Robin Gurland]]"
*:<small>How do you find a young Owen Lars more than 20 years after the elder Owen makes his screen debut? Is Hayden Christensen really as great as everybody says he is? [[Robin Gurland]], Casting Director for Episode II, dishes on the casting process.</small>
*"[[Area Film Satirized—Star Wars in the Onion|Area Film Satirized—''Star Wars'' in the Onion]]" {{C|by Scott Chernoff}}
*:<small>If you haven't read ''The Onion'', you're just not trying. This timely, hilarious parody newspaper makes fun of every American event that comes along. Needless to say, that can't fail to include ''Star Wars''. Scott Chernoff gives us the scoop.</small>

